{"type":"tool_result","timestamp":"2026-04-26T04:45:43.906Z","tool_id":"run_shell_command_1777178743714_0","status":"success","output":"commit 0345b299714d30cb3f1f7c480fa9eb4edccad83d (HEAD -> feat/graceful-degradation)\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Sat Apr 25 21:44:14 2026 -0700\n\n    feat(sampler): add post-piece hook that writes usage journal entries [T-022@20260425T183959Zc]\n    \n    Adds `post_piece_hook(tracker, arc_payoff_score, journal_path)` and\n    `derive_arc_payoff_summary(...)` to `senseweave.usage_journal`. The hook\n    consumes the active `SampleUsageTracker`, derives a banded textual\n    arc-payoff summary (weak/moderate/strong + score + sample count), folds\n    the accumulated plays into a `JournalEntry`, and appends it to the\n    journal file. Tests cover summary banding, hook invocation + on-disk\n    output, multi-piece appends, and the no-active-piece error path.\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n my-claw/tools/senseweave/usage_journal.py | 37 +++++++++++++\n tests/test_usage_journal.py               | 86 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n 2 files changed, 123 insertions(+)\n\ncommit 0c669c41b536a2da7efc4ba7b275c2abeb647e04\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Sat Apr 25 21:39:58 2026 -0700\n\n    verify(T-022@20260425T183959Zb): PASS — SampleUsageTracker accumulation verified\n\n progress.md                                        | 18 ++++++++-----\n sdp/notifications.log                              | 13 ++++++++++\n sdp/run-log.md                                     | 14 +++++++++-\n sdp/verification/t-022@20260425t183959zb-verify.md | 30 ++++++++++++++++++++++\n 4 files changed, 67 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)\n\ncommit b8b3ac70ea647da0cf52994639bf428e55ff611b\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Sat Apr 25 21:38:14 2026 -0700\n\n    feat(sampler): add SampleUsageTracker for piece playback [T-022@20260425T183959